    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>There are none (at least in the standard Java library). Character sets vary from platform to platform so there isn't a standard list of them in Java.</p>\n\n<p>There are some 3rd party libraries which contain these constants though. One of these is Guava (Google core libraries): <a href=\"http://guava-libraries.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/javadoc/com/google/common/base/Charsets.html\">http://guava-libraries.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/javadoc/com/google/common/base/Charsets.html</a></p>\n"
  }, {
