  "question_id" : 6698354,
  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/6698354/894where-to-get-utf-8-string-literal-in-java",
  "title" : "894@Where to get &quot;UTF-8&quot; string literal in Java?",
  "body" : "<p>I'm trying to use a constant instead of a string literal in this piece of code:</p>\n<pre><code>new InputStreamReader(new FileInputStream(file), &quot;UTF-8&quot;)\n</code></pre>\n<p><code>&quot;UTF-8&quot;</code> appears in the code rather often, and would be much better to refer to some <code>static final</code> variable instead. Do you know where I can find such a variable in JDK?</p>\n"
}